    schema1:description "Prof Chris Hyde qualified in Medicine from the University of London in 1986 and completed specialist training in public health in 1994. He has been a Chair of Public Health and Clinical Epidemiology at the University of Exeter since 2009. He leads the Exeter Test Group."@en ;
